WEBVTT

00:00:33.241 --> 00:00:37.954
AGENT KIM: REBOOT[cite: 1]

00:00:39.122 --> 00:00:41.166
EPISODE 1[cite: 1]

00:01:05.523 --> 00:01:07.067
Are you kidding me?[cite: 1]

00:01:07.150 --> 00:01:10.278
Move your car! You're blocking the way![cite: 1]

00:01:10.361 --> 00:01:11.446
Oh my god.[cite: 1]

00:01:15.492 --> 00:01:16.951
Geez, if you're in a hurry, just walk.[cite: 1]

00:01:17.035 --> 00:01:18.536
I'm so hungry. When is the food coming?[cite: 1]

00:01:18.620 --> 00:01:20.747
I know. It's taking forever.[cite: 1]

00:01:23.500 --> 00:01:25.460
Can we get our food first?[cite: 1]

00:01:50.235 --> 00:01:51.611
You're drunk![cite: 1]

00:01:54.989 --> 00:01:55.824
What is that?[cite: 1]

00:01:57.367 --> 00:01:59.828
Damn it. What the hell?[cite: 1]

00:02:01.204 --> 00:02:03.331
Hey, you. Come here.[cite: 1]

00:02:03.414 --> 00:02:05.542
Shit, it's broken.[cite: 1]

00:02:05.625 --> 00:02:07.585
Fucking hell. Get over here.[cite: 1]

00:02:08.878 --> 00:02:10.547
Hey, I said come here![cite: 1]

00:02:11.673 --> 00:02:12.799
Where do you think you're going?[cite: 1]

00:02:12.882 --> 00:02:14.384
Hey![cite: 1]

00:02:14.467 --> 00:02:15.718
Who do you think you are?[cite: 1]

00:02:15.802 --> 00:02:18.221
Trying to pull an insurance scam or what?[cite: 1]

00:02:18.304 --> 00:02:20.014
When you bump into someone else's car,[cite: 1]

00:02:20.098 --> 00:02:25.186
you're supposed to get on your knees
and beg for forgiveness.[cite: 1]

00:02:25.270 --> 00:02:27.188
This whole thing needs to be replaced.[cite: 1]

00:02:27.272 --> 00:02:28.773
Who knows how much this will cost.[cite: 1]

00:02:28.857 --> 00:02:30.733
I think my arm is fine,[cite: 1]

00:02:31.359 --> 00:02:32.569
so you can just go.[cite: 1]

00:02:33.361 --> 00:02:35.738
Hey, I can't believe this guy.[cite: 1]

00:02:36.364 --> 00:02:39.200
I'm really fine, you can leave.[cite: 1]

00:02:40.243 --> 00:02:42.871
Are you being serious right now?[cite: 1]

00:02:42.954 --> 00:02:45.623
Are you out of your mind?[cite: 1]

00:02:45.707 --> 00:02:46.749
Do you have a death wish?[cite: 1]

00:02:49.377 --> 00:02:50.253
What?[cite: 1]

00:02:53.548 --> 00:02:54.507
What are you looking at?[cite: 1]

00:02:59.596 --> 00:03:00.597
I'm sorry.[cite: 1]

00:03:02.140 --> 00:03:03.433
I'm truly sorry.[cite: 1]

00:03:03.516 --> 00:03:04.475
It's too late for that.[cite: 1]

00:03:04.559 --> 00:03:06.102
Try saying it again.[cite: 1]

00:03:06.185 --> 00:03:08.438
Come on, let's go. It's late.[cite: 1]

00:03:08.521 --> 00:03:09.355
Let's go.[cite: 1]

00:03:10.356 --> 00:03:11.274
Just go, then.[cite: 1]

00:03:11.858 --> 00:03:13.026
I accept your apology.[cite: 1]

00:03:13.943 --> 00:03:15.069
Let's call it even with this.[cite: 1]

00:03:17.155 --> 00:03:19.866
Wow, have you been working out lately?[cite: 1]

00:03:19.949 --> 00:03:21.576
- Hell of a punch.[cite: 1]
- Is he dead?[cite: 1]

00:03:21.659 --> 00:03:23.745
- Should we get him a blanket?[cite: 1]
- Damn it![cite: 1]

00:04:01.407 --> 00:04:03.284
AGENT KIM: REBOOT[cite: 1]

00:04:03.868 --> 00:04:05.078
Good morning![cite: 1]

00:04:05.161 --> 00:04:06.454
Looks like you missed a button.[cite: 1]

00:04:06.537 --> 00:04:07.622
- No, I didn't.[cite: 1]
- Are you sure?[cite: 1]

00:04:08.414 --> 00:04:10.083
Let me brush that dust off for you.[cite: 1]

00:04:10.166 --> 00:04:11.251
No, it's fine.[cite: 1]

00:04:11.334 --> 00:04:13.169
- Let me get that.[cite: 1]
- Thank you.[cite: 1]

00:04:42.448 --> 00:04:43.741
WHEN YOUR CHILD REACHES ADOLESCENCE[cite: 1]

00:05:22.155 --> 00:05:23.239
KIM MIN JI[cite: 1]

00:05:40.381 --> 00:05:41.507
AUTHORIZED PERSONNEL ONLY[cite: 1]

00:05:41.591 --> 00:05:43.634
Min Ji, wake up.[cite: 1]

00:05:47.597 --> 00:05:48.806
NO ENTRY. YOU ENTER, YOU DIE![cite: 1]

00:05:49.932 --> 00:05:50.850
Min Ji.[cite: 1]

00:05:57.065 --> 00:05:59.275
Kim Min Ji, you're going to be late for school![cite: 1]

00:05:59.776 --> 00:06:01.652
- It's time to...[cite: 1]
- Stop talking about breakfast![cite: 1]

00:06:02.904 --> 00:06:06.491
No one is going to yell at you
if I skip breakfast![cite: 1]

00:06:07.325 --> 00:06:09.118
Stop laughing![cite: 1]

00:06:09.202 --> 00:06:10.453
You're a student,[cite: 1]

00:06:10.536 --> 00:06:12.622
you need to eat a proper meal
before going to school.[cite: 1]

00:06:17.335 --> 00:06:18.628
Kim Min Ji![cite: 1]

00:06:26.469 --> 00:06:28.805
SCHOOL NOTICE[cite: 1]
EMERGENCY CONTACT FORM[cite: 1]

00:06:34.143 --> 00:06:35.561
MOTHER: X[cite: 1]
SIBLINGS: X[cite: 1]

00:06:35.645 --> 00:06:36.479
Hey, Min Ji.[cite: 1]

00:06:36.562 --> 00:06:38.189
I need the name of a close friend[cite: 1]

00:06:38.272 --> 00:06:40.066
and their phone number.[cite: 1]

00:06:42.151 --> 00:06:43.444
Kim Min Ji![cite: 1]

00:06:43.528 --> 00:06:44.529
Kang Hye Ryeong.[cite: 1]

00:06:44.612 --> 00:06:46.948
The number is 010-0610-6003.[cite: 1]

00:06:49.617 --> 00:06:51.702
I filled out the form. Have something to eat.[cite: 1]

00:06:51.786 --> 00:06:52.620
I'm late.[cite: 1]

00:06:52.703 --> 00:06:54.997
- Your report card...[cite: 1]
- Don't look at it![cite: 1]

00:06:55.081 --> 00:06:58.376
- 8th place? How did this happen?[cite: 1]
- The higher the rank, the better.[cite: 1]

00:06:58.459 --> 00:07:00.128
- Right?[cite: 1]
- The rules changed.[cite: 1]

00:07:00.211 --> 00:07:01.295
I told you before.[cite: 1]

00:07:01.379 --> 00:07:03.297
- Don't study too hard.[cite: 1]
- Yeah.[cite: 1]

00:07:06.968 --> 00:07:07.802
Kang...[cite: 1]

00:07:08.469 --> 00:07:09.345
Hye...[cite: 1]

00:07:10.680 --> 00:07:11.556
Ryeong.[cite: 1]

00:07:21.107 --> 00:07:22.608
LAUNDROMAT[cite: 1]

00:07:22.692 --> 00:07:23.693
Min Ji![cite: 1]

00:07:24.819 --> 00:07:25.736
Min Ji![cite: 1]

00:07:26.446 --> 00:07:27.613
- Hello, sir.[cite: 1]
- Hey.[cite: 1]

00:07:27.697 --> 00:07:28.865
How is your dad doing?[cite: 1]

00:07:28.948 --> 00:07:31.284
- What do you mean?[cite: 1]
- Well, those thugs...[cite: 1]

00:07:32.285 --> 00:07:33.327
Never mind.[cite: 1]

00:07:33.411 --> 00:07:35.746
By the way, why don't you get your uniform altered?[cite: 1]

00:07:35.830 --> 00:07:38.458
I'm an expert at alterations, you know.[cite: 1]

00:07:38.541 --> 00:07:40.710
No thanks. I don't know
when I'll have to transfer schools again.[cite: 1]

00:07:41.461 --> 00:07:42.378
The bus is here.[cite: 1]

00:07:42.462 --> 00:07:43.546
What?[cite: 1]

00:07:51.137 --> 00:07:52.096
Have a good day.[cite: 1]

00:07:52.638 --> 00:07:56.350
Goodness, her uniform
is always ironed so perfectly.[cite: 1]

00:07:59.353 --> 00:08:01.147
Mr. Kim![cite: 1]

00:08:01.230 --> 00:08:02.857
Are you okay?[cite: 1]

00:08:02.940 --> 00:08:04.358
You look fine.[cite: 1]

00:08:04.442 --> 00:08:06.277
I saw those thugs messing with you the other night.[cite: 1]

00:08:06.360 --> 00:08:08.321
I'm sorry I didn't step in.[cite: 1]

00:08:08.404 --> 00:08:10.031
I'm a bit of a coward.[cite: 1]

00:08:10.114 --> 00:08:11.699
I would have done the same in your shoes.[cite: 1]

00:08:12.992 --> 00:08:14.869
Oh man, Mr. Kim.[cite: 1]

00:08:14.952 --> 00:08:17.330
You really should iron
your suit.[cite: 1]

00:08:17.413 --> 00:08:20.541
That's what laundromats are for.[cite: 1]

00:08:20.625 --> 00:08:23.920
Come on, you live right above
a laundromat.[cite: 1]

00:08:24.003 --> 00:08:26.047
That hurts my pride.[cite: 1]

00:08:26.797 --> 00:08:28.216
I'll bring it down next time.[cite: 1]

00:08:28.299 --> 00:08:31.177
I can iron it for you
in a flash. Come on in.[cite: 1]

00:08:31.260 --> 00:08:32.762
- Let's go.[cite: 1]
- I have to catch my bus.[cite: 1]

00:08:32.845 --> 00:08:34.430
Let me iron that for you first.[cite: 1]

00:08:34.514 --> 00:08:35.723
Hold on.[cite: 1]

00:08:36.516 --> 00:08:37.725
Mr. Kim.[cite: 1]

00:08:37.808 --> 00:08:38.684
Mr. Kim![cite: 1]

00:08:40.520 --> 00:08:43.397
Geez. Like father, like daughter.[cite: 1]

00:08:43.481 --> 00:08:45.399
They are exactly the same.[cite: 1]

00:08:46.609 --> 00:08:48.903
My sales pitch
doesn't work on them.[cite: 1]

00:08:52.615 --> 00:08:53.449
Wait![cite: 1]

00:08:53.533 --> 00:08:54.742
Thank you.[cite: 1]

00:09:17.974 --> 00:09:20.101
Excuse me, coming through.[cite: 1]

00:09:24.272 --> 00:09:26.232
Stop pushing![cite: 1]

00:09:50.423 --> 00:09:51.507
You guys are going to get hurt.[cite: 1]

00:09:51.591 --> 00:09:53.843
SCHOOL VIOLENCE[cite: 1]
DON'T IGNORE IT, PROTECT THE VICTIMS![cite: 1]

00:09:54.427 --> 00:09:56.387
- Did you have breakfast?[cite: 1]
- Yes, sir.[cite: 1]

00:09:56.470 --> 00:09:58.014
- Good morning, sir.[cite: 1]
- Good morning.[cite: 1]

00:09:58.097 --> 00:09:59.557
- This is how you bow.[cite: 1]
- That's right.[cite: 1]

00:10:05.104 --> 00:10:06.981
SANGSAENG SAVINGS BANK[cite: 1]

00:10:08.649 --> 00:10:10.568
Morning, Manager Kim. You're always the first one here.[cite: 1]

00:10:10.651 --> 00:10:11.527
Good morning.[cite: 1]

00:10:12.653 --> 00:10:15.489
SAVINGS BANK[cite: 1]
LOAN REGISTRATION & COUNSELING SUPPORT[cite: 1]

00:10:20.244 --> 00:10:22.038
Customer number 155, please.[cite: 1]

00:10:26.250 --> 00:10:27.501
CORPORATE CARD EXPENSES[cite: 1]

00:10:27.585 --> 00:10:28.836
SEOREUNG COMPANY / CHINESE FOOD[cite: 1]

00:10:31.631 --> 00:10:33.090
REQUESTER: KANG HAK SU[cite: 1]
DEPARTMENT: TREASURY[cite: 1]

00:10:34.383 --> 00:10:35.217
LEAVE HISTORY[cite: 1]

00:10:42.808 --> 00:10:46.562
I was reviewing your expense report and...[cite: 1]

00:10:47.772 --> 00:10:48.689
Sir.[cite: 1]

00:10:48.773 --> 00:10:49.815
What is it?[cite: 1]

00:10:49.899 --> 00:10:52.234
These are the corporate card
expenses.[cite: 1]

00:10:52.318 --> 00:10:56.405
You charged 95,000 won for Chinese food
last Wednesday.[cite: 1]

00:10:56.489 --> 00:10:57.490
So?[cite: 1]

00:10:57.573 --> 00:11:01.118
You took the day off
for your wedding anniversary that day.[cite: 1]

00:11:01.202 --> 00:11:03.746
The receipt is also missing,
so maybe there was a mistake?[cite: 1]

00:11:04.955 --> 00:11:07.083
Hey Kim, do you eat a lot of fish
for your brain?[cite: 1]

00:11:07.667 --> 00:11:08.501
Excuse me?[cite: 1]

00:11:08.584 --> 00:11:09.669
Why is your memory so good?[cite: 1]

00:11:09.752 --> 00:11:14.382
I do try to eat a lot of fish.
I especially like mackerel.[cite: 1]

00:11:15.257 --> 00:11:17.259
Cut down on the mackerel and saury,[cite: 1]

00:11:17.343 --> 00:11:20.221
and learn to bend the rules instead.[cite: 1]

00:11:20.304 --> 00:11:21.472
You need to be more flexible.[cite: 1]

00:11:22.473 --> 00:11:24.683
Just put it down as
corporate entertainment expenses.[cite: 1]

00:11:28.020 --> 00:11:28.854
Yes, sir.[cite: 1]

00:11:29.480 --> 00:11:31.524
I will list it as
corporate entertainment expenses.[cite: 1]

00:11:32.191 --> 00:11:36.821
Thank you so much
for remembering my wedding anniversary.[cite: 1]

00:11:36.904 --> 00:11:37.780
You're welcome.[cite: 1]

00:11:41.158 --> 00:11:43.244
Jeez, he's such a pain.[cite: 1]

00:11:44.578 --> 00:11:46.080
PLEASE PROCEED TO THE NEXT COUNTER[cite: 1]

00:11:50.459 --> 00:11:51.585
Let's call it even with this.[cite: 1]

00:11:56.382 --> 00:11:59.301
SELF-DEFENSE TOOLS[cite: 1]

00:12:01.846 --> 00:12:05.266
Do I really have to pre-order and wait in a long line
just to buy some desserts?[cite: 1]

00:12:05.349 --> 00:12:06.475
What time does it start?[cite: 1]

00:12:12.189 --> 00:12:13.899
- Mr. Kim.[cite: 1]
- Oh my, you startled me![cite: 1]

00:12:13.983 --> 00:12:15.025
What is it, Sang A?[cite: 1]

00:12:15.609 --> 00:12:17.862
Is something wrong?
Why are you looking at self-defense tools?[cite: 1]

00:12:17.945 --> 00:12:19.780
Oh, it's nothing.[cite: 1]

00:12:20.656 --> 00:12:22.741
Wait, are you planning to use that at night...[cite: 1]

00:12:24.493 --> 00:12:25.870
to take care of Manager Kang?[cite: 1]

00:12:25.953 --> 00:12:27.246
Manager Kang?[cite: 1]

00:12:27.329 --> 00:12:28.164
Of course not.[cite: 1]

00:12:29.290 --> 00:12:30.666
It's not that.[cite: 1]

00:12:30.749 --> 00:12:32.877
My neighborhood hasn't felt very safe lately.[cite: 1]

00:12:35.588 --> 00:12:36.589
Hey, Sang A.[cite: 1]

00:12:36.672 --> 00:12:39.091
Does this look useful to you?[cite: 1]

00:12:39.175 --> 00:12:41.719
It's easy to carry and looks effective.[cite: 1]

00:12:42.928 --> 00:12:44.013
Are you buying it for yourself?[cite: 1]

00:12:44.096 --> 00:12:45.347
It's meant for women.[cite: 1]

00:12:45.431 --> 00:12:47.391
Min Ji's birthday is coming up.[cite: 1]

00:12:47.475 --> 00:12:49.393
Oh, it's your daughter's birthday.[cite: 1]

00:12:49.477 --> 00:12:50.561
How old is she?[cite: 1]

00:12:51.604 --> 00:12:52.605
She's a junior in high school.[cite: 1]

00:12:54.773 --> 00:12:56.984
A self-defense tool for a high school girl...[cite: 1]

00:12:59.236 --> 00:13:02.281
Why don't you just ask her
what she wants?[cite: 1]

00:13:02.364 --> 00:13:03.908
I'd love to,[cite: 1]

00:13:03.991 --> 00:13:06.410
but lately
she won't even talk to me.[cite: 1]

00:13:06.494 --> 00:13:07.953
She keeps avoiding me.[cite: 1]

00:13:08.454 --> 00:13:10.331
It seems she's going through a late rebellious phase.[cite: 1]

00:13:10.414 --> 00:13:12.833
Don't worry too much.
Every kid goes through that at her age.[cite: 1]

00:13:13.876 --> 00:13:16.045
Maybe things would be better
if her mom were here.[cite: 1]

00:13:20.257 --> 00:13:23.093
I'll help you pick out a gift.[cite: 1]

00:13:23.886 --> 00:13:26.222
- Really?[cite: 1]
- I'm heading to the department store anyway.[cite: 1]

00:13:26.305 --> 00:13:27.556
Let's go together after work.[cite: 1]

00:13:28.641 --> 00:13:29.600
No, you don't have to...[cite: 1]

00:13:29.683 --> 00:13:31.727
We'll leave at exactly six o'clock.[cite: 1]

00:13:36.065 --> 00:13:37.316
Hey, Kim Min Ji.[cite: 1]

00:13:37.399 --> 00:13:38.484
Min Ji.[cite: 1]

00:13:38.567 --> 00:13:39.693
Let me borrow your PE uniform.[cite: 1]

00:13:39.777 --> 00:13:43.322
Hye Ryeong, you didn't even return it last time,
I had to look all over for you.[cite: 1]

00:13:43.405 --> 00:13:46.367
Come on, we're friends.
I'm begging you.[cite: 1]

00:13:48.452 --> 00:13:49.286
What's this?[cite: 1]

00:13:52.081 --> 00:13:53.624
Thanks. I'll return it right away.[cite: 1]

00:14:01.215 --> 00:14:02.883
Geez, wash your clothes.[cite: 1]

00:14:04.301 --> 00:14:05.719
Hey, Ju Hye Ri, what is that?[cite: 1]

00:14:06.804 --> 00:14:08.347
My dad bought it on his business trip.[cite: 1]

00:14:08.430 --> 00:14:09.848
It's so pretty.[cite: 1]

00:14:09.932 --> 00:14:12.643
- I've never seen this model from that brand before.[cite: 1]
- Me neither.[cite: 1]

00:14:12.726 --> 00:14:13.811
It's not sold in Korea.[cite: 1]

00:14:13.894 --> 00:14:15.062
It's a limited edition.[cite: 1]

00:14:15.813 --> 00:14:17.648
Mine is just a cheap brand.[cite: 1]

00:14:17.731 --> 00:14:20.985
- I'm so jealous of you, Hye Ri.[cite: 1]
- Yeah, yours looks really cheap.[cite: 1]

00:14:21.068 --> 00:14:21.902
Is that so?[cite: 1]

00:14:21.986 --> 00:14:24.989
- How much was that?[cite: 1]
- 5,000 won.[cite: 1]

00:14:25.072 --> 00:14:25.948
What's her problem?[cite: 1]

00:14:27.116 --> 00:14:28.075
Is she crazy?[cite: 1]

00:14:28.158 --> 00:14:29.243
Just ignore her.[cite: 1]

00:14:29.326 --> 00:14:30.578
Let her be.[cite: 1]

00:14:30.661 --> 00:14:32.288
You'll end up smelling like a widower old man.[cite: 1]

00:14:34.039 --> 00:14:35.332
Hey, there's Kim Nam Hoon.[cite: 1]

00:14:35.416 --> 00:14:38.460
He doesn't even try to hide
that he's here to see Hye Ri anymore.[cite: 1]

00:14:39.545 --> 00:14:40.963
Hye Ri, do you have a minute?[cite: 1]

00:14:56.896 --> 00:14:57.938
Hey, buddy.[cite: 1]

00:15:00.900 --> 00:15:01.734
GIRLS[cite: 1]

00:15:02.318 --> 00:15:03.861
Hey, what flavor is that?[cite: 1]

00:15:03.944 --> 00:15:04.862
Grape.[cite: 1]

00:15:04.945 --> 00:15:06.530
- Can I try it?[cite: 1]
- No.[cite: 1]

00:15:06.614 --> 00:15:08.324
- Just one puff.[cite: 1]
- Smoke your own.[cite: 1]

00:15:08.407 --> 00:15:09.283
Fine.[cite: 1]

00:15:09.783 --> 00:15:11.493
- Just one more drag.[cite: 1]
- No.[cite: 1]

00:15:12.328 --> 00:15:13.454
- Let's trade.[cite: 1]
- No.[cite: 1]

00:15:13.537 --> 00:15:16.624
- Come on, just for today.[cite: 1]
- I said I don't want to![cite: 1]

00:15:16.707 --> 00:15:17.708
Hey.[cite: 1]

00:15:19.460 --> 00:15:21.587
Damn it, it smells like a widower old man in here.[cite: 1]

00:15:22.838 --> 00:15:25.341
The smell of cigarettes on you
is even more disgusting.[cite: 1]

00:15:27.801 --> 00:15:29.011
What did you just say?[cite: 1]

00:15:30.429 --> 00:15:31.805
I'm asking you.[cite: 1]

00:15:32.681 --> 00:15:33.849
Don't look at me like that.[cite: 1]

00:15:33.933 --> 00:15:35.392
I told you not to look at me like that![cite: 1]

00:15:35.476 --> 00:15:36.560
Hey![cite: 1]

00:15:37.269 --> 00:15:38.520
That's enough.[cite: 1]

00:15:39.647 --> 00:15:42.358
Stop picking fights
with that pathetic loser.[cite: 1]

00:15:43.901 --> 00:15:45.152
Why am I pathetic?[cite: 1]

00:15:53.744 --> 00:15:56.372
I mean, look at yourself.[cite: 1]

00:15:56.872 --> 00:15:58.040
You're incredibly pathetic.[cite: 1]

00:16:18.644 --> 00:16:21.772
SANGSAENG SAVINGS BANK[cite: 1]

00:16:25.567 --> 00:16:26.610
Mr. Kim![cite: 1]

00:16:27.987 --> 00:16:30.322
- Hey Sang A.[cite: 1]
- Let's go buy a present for your daughter.[cite: 1]

00:16:31.115 --> 00:16:32.366
Were you being serious earlier?[cite: 1]

00:16:32.950 --> 00:16:34.368
Are you really asking? I'm hurt.[cite: 1]

00:16:35.202 --> 00:16:37.746
I mean, are you sure?
I don't want to bother you.[cite: 1]

00:16:37.830 --> 00:16:39.456
If you don't want to, it's fine.[cite: 1]

00:16:39.540 --> 00:16:40.541
Goodbye then.[cite: 1]

00:16:44.003 --> 00:16:45.045
Sang A![cite: 1]

00:16:45.129 --> 00:16:46.422
Wait.[cite: 1]

00:16:55.931 --> 00:16:56.765
Sang A.[cite: 1]

00:17:07.693 --> 00:17:08.527
It's over there.[cite: 1]

00:17:13.198 --> 00:17:14.116
PRE-ORDER PICKUP[cite: 1]

00:17:17.703 --> 00:17:19.288
- What the hell is this?[cite: 1]
- Mr. Kim.[cite: 1]

00:17:20.414 --> 00:17:21.457
What's this?[cite: 1]

00:17:23.042 --> 00:17:24.668
- Give me your credit card.[cite: 1]
- Mine?[cite: 1]

00:17:24.752 --> 00:17:26.170
It will take longer if we go together.[cite: 1]

00:17:26.253 --> 00:17:29.548
You just wait in line here
while I go buy a gift for your daughter.[cite: 1]

00:17:29.631 --> 00:17:31.008
It's a win-win situation.[cite: 1]

00:17:37.681 --> 00:17:40.976
I sent you a screenshot
of my pre-order,[cite: 1]

00:17:41.060 --> 00:17:42.853
so when it's your turn, just pick up the item.[cite: 1]

00:17:44.063 --> 00:17:44.897
Screenshot?[cite: 1]

00:17:46.106 --> 00:17:46.940
Wait a minute.[cite: 1]

00:17:50.069 --> 00:17:52.571
My phone
can't view images.[cite: 1]

00:18:08.545 --> 00:18:10.756
How many zeros are there?[cite: 1]

00:18:11.548 --> 00:18:12.508
What? 500,000 won?[cite: 1]

00:18:12.591 --> 00:18:14.426
Next person, please.[cite: 1]

00:18:15.844 --> 00:18:16.762
Oh, yes.[cite: 1]

00:18:16.845 --> 00:18:18.347
I need to confirm a pre-order.[cite: 1]

00:18:20.182 --> 00:18:22.059
It's under the name Jung Sang A.[cite: 1]

00:18:22.142 --> 00:18:24.978
Not the name.
I need to see the Order Number.[cite: 1]

00:18:25.062 --> 00:18:26.230
What's an Order Number?[cite: 1]

00:18:26.313 --> 00:18:29.233
Unconfirmed pre-orders
must move to the walk-in line.[cite: 1]

00:18:30.859 --> 00:18:31.693
WALK-INS[cite: 1]

00:18:34.321 --> 00:18:36.031
But she said she pre-ordered...[cite: 1]

00:18:36.115 --> 00:18:38.534
- Next person, please.[cite: 1]
- Oh man, come on.[cite: 1]

00:18:40.160 --> 00:18:40.994
Here.[cite: 1]

00:18:41.954 --> 00:18:43.956
Yes, ma'am, you're all set.[cite: 1]

00:18:44.039 --> 00:18:44.873
Thank you.[cite: 1]

00:18:49.253 --> 00:18:52.464
Come on, Mr. Kim.
It's your daughter's birthday today.[cite: 1]

00:18:53.257 --> 00:18:55.467
I'm sorry, but I'd like a refund.[cite: 1]

00:18:55.551 --> 00:18:57.678
Please wait a moment.[cite: 1]

00:19:01.849 --> 00:19:04.685
I always stay up-to-date
with the current trends, you know.[cite: 1]

00:19:04.768 --> 00:19:07.855
This is the hottest trend these days.
Just trust me and buy it.[cite: 1]

00:19:07.938 --> 00:19:09.731
My daughter is in high school.[cite: 1]

00:19:09.815 --> 00:19:12.943
It makes no sense for a high schooler
to wear a 500,000 won T-shirt.[cite: 1]

00:19:13.819 --> 00:19:15.946
- Please help me get a refund.[cite: 1]
- Yes, it is expensive.[cite: 1]

00:19:16.029 --> 00:19:19.825
But this is a secret weapon
to help her get through her rebellious phase.[cite: 1]

00:19:19.908 --> 00:19:22.369
Imagine the worst-case scenario.[cite: 1]

00:19:22.870 --> 00:19:23.704
"Worst-case"?[cite: 1]

00:19:23.787 --> 00:19:25.664
"As a dad, what have you ever done for me?"[cite: 1]

00:19:26.623 --> 00:19:29.585
If she says that, your relationship
is over right then and there.[cite: 1]

00:19:29.668 --> 00:19:33.589
You have to do something really big
to prepare for the worst-case scenario[cite: 1]

00:19:33.672 --> 00:19:35.382
and hit her back with a badass line.[cite: 1]

00:19:36.008 --> 00:19:38.135
"I bought you
a 500,000 won T-shirt!"[cite: 1]

00:19:41.305 --> 00:19:42.306
Something like that.[cite: 1]

00:19:42.389 --> 00:19:44.266
This is really popular with kids these days.[cite: 1]

00:19:44.933 --> 00:19:48.020
She'll think: "My old-fashioned dad
is actually pretty cool."[cite: 1]

00:19:48.729 --> 00:19:50.189
I bet she'll see you differently.[cite: 1]

00:20:44.785 --> 00:20:46.620
Min Ji, I'm home.[cite: 1]

00:20:48.747 --> 00:20:50.123
Since when have you been home?[cite: 1]

00:20:52.834 --> 00:20:54.002
What are you doing?[cite: 1]

00:20:56.129 --> 00:20:56.964
Kim Min Ji.[cite: 1]

00:20:57.589 --> 00:20:58.507
I'm talking to you.[cite: 1]

00:20:59.341 --> 00:21:01.885
From now on, don't
wash your clothes with mine.[cite: 1]

00:21:01.969 --> 00:21:03.679
It makes my clothes smell like an old man.[cite: 1]

00:21:11.311 --> 00:21:12.437
Alright.[cite: 1]

00:21:12.521 --> 00:21:13.522
Then from now on,[cite: 1]

00:21:14.273 --> 00:21:15.357
you wash your own clothes.[cite: 1]

00:22:04.823 --> 00:22:05.782
TAGGED[cite: 1]

00:22:06.283 --> 00:22:07.242
KIM NAM HOON[cite: 1]

00:22:19.588 --> 00:22:22.674
Wait, how can I unlike this?[cite: 1]

00:22:23.633 --> 00:22:24.718
Who are you?[cite: 1]

00:22:35.437 --> 00:22:36.605
Oh, geez.[cite: 1]

00:22:49.117 --> 00:22:49.951
Dad.[cite: 1]

00:22:58.752 --> 00:22:59.878
Go to your room and sleep.[cite: 1]

00:23:02.005 --> 00:23:02.839
What is it, Min Ji?[cite: 1]

00:23:02.923 --> 00:23:04.424
I said go to your room and sleep.[cite: 1]

00:23:05.008 --> 00:23:05.842
Right.[cite: 1]

00:23:17.062 --> 00:23:17.896
Dad.[cite: 1]

00:23:20.816 --> 00:23:21.650
Yeah?[cite: 1]

00:23:25.320 --> 00:23:26.738
About what I said earlier...[cite: 1]

00:23:26.822 --> 00:23:29.074
You forgot to wash the dishes.[cite: 1]

00:23:31.451 --> 00:23:33.120
I can wash them tomorrow morning.[cite: 1]

00:23:33.203 --> 00:23:35.122
Just go to sleep.[cite: 1]

00:23:39.584 --> 00:23:41.670
Yeah. You should go to sleep too.[cite: 1]

00:23:53.098 --> 00:23:54.432
Good morning![cite: 1]

00:23:54.516 --> 00:23:56.434
Looks like you missed a button.[cite: 1]

00:23:56.518 --> 00:23:57.519
Are you sure you're okay?[cite: 1]

00:23:57.602 --> 00:23:59.020
DOWON LAUNDROMAT[cite: 1]

00:24:23.628 --> 00:24:24.754
What's up with her?[cite: 1]

00:24:27.799 --> 00:24:29.050
Alright, then...[cite: 1]

00:24:30.510 --> 00:24:32.262
I'll make Min Ji's favorite dish.[cite: 1]

00:24:33.180 --> 00:24:34.598
Soy sauce egg rice.[cite: 1]

00:24:45.150 --> 00:24:46.943
- Hey![cite: 1]
- I need my PE uniform.[cite: 1]

00:25:07.464 --> 00:25:09.090
Did you see her face just now?[cite: 1]

00:25:12.344 --> 00:25:14.846
- Hye Ryeong, wake up.[cite: 1]
- What?[cite: 1]

00:25:14.930 --> 00:25:17.057
I have PE next period. Where's my uniform?[cite: 1]

00:25:17.140 --> 00:25:18.475
I already returned it to you.[cite: 1]

00:25:18.558 --> 00:25:20.852
When? I haven't gotten it.[cite: 1]

00:25:20.936 --> 00:25:22.938
I put it on your desk.[cite: 1]

00:25:26.149 --> 00:25:27.150
Hurry up.[cite: 1]

00:25:29.277 --> 00:25:30.487
Hey, Min Ji.[cite: 1]

00:25:30.570 --> 00:25:32.155
Check the trash can.[cite: 1]

00:25:39.996 --> 00:25:41.957
KIM MIN JI[cite: 1]

00:26:01.393 --> 00:26:03.061
Did you see her face just now?[cite: 1]

00:26:24.291 --> 00:26:26.584
I just played volleyball,
so it might smell like sweat.[cite: 1]

00:26:27.127 --> 00:26:27.961
What?[cite: 1]

00:26:35.093 --> 00:26:37.387
A five-on-five match
starts in ten minutes![cite: 1]

00:26:37.470 --> 00:26:39.389
The losing team gets cleaning duty for a month.[cite: 1]

00:26:40.432 --> 00:26:41.266
Min Ji.[cite: 1]

00:26:41.808 --> 00:26:42.934
Kim Min Ji, come here.[cite: 1]

00:26:43.810 --> 00:26:44.894
Why are you only wearing half

00:26:45.687 --> 00:26:46.813
of your PE uniform?[cite: 1]

00:26:46.896 --> 00:26:48.773
Planning to play basketball in a skirt?[cite: 1]

00:26:48.857 --> 00:26:50.275
- I forgot them, sir.[cite: 1]
- "Kim Nam Hoon"?[cite: 1]

00:26:51.276 --> 00:26:52.944
Didn't Nam Hoon lend you pants?[cite: 1]

00:27:00.035 --> 00:27:01.953
Now, double punch combination! One![cite: 1]

00:27:02.037 --> 00:27:03.496
- Taekwon![cite: 1]
- Taekwon![cite: 1]

00:27:03.580 --> 00:27:04.414
Two![cite: 1]

00:27:04.497 --> 00:27:06.249
- Taekwon![cite: 1]
- Taekwon![cite: 1]

00:27:06.333 --> 00:27:07.959
Now, triple punch combination! One![cite: 1]

00:27:08.043 --> 00:27:10.003
- Taekwondo![cite: 1]
- Taekwondo![cite: 1]

00:27:10.086 --> 00:27:10.920
Two![cite: 1]

00:27:11.004 --> 00:27:12.630
- Taekwondo![cite: 1]
- Taekwondo![cite: 1]

00:27:12.714 --> 00:27:13.590
Return to ready stance![cite: 1]

00:27:13.673 --> 00:27:15.633
Kicking stance, ready![cite: 1]

00:27:16.801 --> 00:27:17.802
One![cite: 1]

00:27:19.471 --> 00:27:20.472
Two![cite: 1]

00:27:21.639 --> 00:27:22.640
Keep your spirit strong![cite: 1]

00:27:22.724 --> 00:27:23.558
Great job![cite: 1]

00:27:23.641 --> 00:27:25.352
Correct footwork! Great.[cite: 1]

00:27:25.435 --> 00:27:26.978
Correct posture![cite: 1]

00:27:27.062 --> 00:27:28.313
Correct...[cite: 1]

00:27:29.397 --> 00:27:30.523
Correct...[cite: 1]

00:27:30.607 --> 00:27:31.566
Correct...[cite: 1]

00:27:31.649 --> 00:27:32.692
Whatever![cite: 1]

00:27:33.526 --> 00:27:35.028
I wasn't done talking.[cite: 1]

00:27:36.738 --> 00:27:38.073
That's it for today.[cite: 1]

00:27:38.156 --> 00:27:39.366
Let's go play![cite: 1]

00:27:42.660 --> 00:27:43.828
Let's go.[cite: 1]

00:27:48.917 --> 00:27:49.751
It's okay.[cite: 1]

00:27:51.169 --> 00:27:52.045
Oh my god.[cite: 1]

00:27:53.671 --> 00:27:57.175
I can't tell if this is a
Taekwondo dojang or a daycare center anymore.[cite: 1]

00:27:57.258 --> 00:27:59.094
Jin Cheol, why are you...[cite: 1]

00:28:00.053 --> 00:28:02.222
Jeez, Jin Cheol. What's wrong with you?[cite: 1]

00:28:02.305 --> 00:28:03.306
Jin Cheol![cite: 1]

00:28:14.901 --> 00:28:15.902
Hey.[cite: 1]

00:28:16.820 --> 00:28:18.154
Who asked him to help?[cite: 1]

00:28:18.238 --> 00:28:20.281
No one asked him.[cite: 1]

00:28:28.456 --> 00:28:29.833
Let's cross the street![cite: 1]

00:28:29.916 --> 00:28:31.709
Come on, kids. Let's cross the street![cite: 1]

00:28:31.793 --> 00:28:33.336
- You can go.[cite: 1]
- Slowly.[cite: 1]

00:28:33.420 --> 00:28:35.171
Let's cross, kids![cite: 1]

00:28:35.255 --> 00:28:37.173
I said go ahead and cross![cite: 1]

00:28:37.257 --> 00:28:39.384
Just go. What's the matter?[cite: 1]

00:28:39.467 --> 00:28:41.010
Why aren't you crossing?[cite: 1]

00:28:41.094 --> 00:28:42.929
- Mom, I'm scared![cite: 1]
- Are you scared of the cars?[cite: 1]

00:28:43.012 --> 00:28:45.014
Oh dear, let me help you.[cite: 1]

00:28:45.098 --> 00:28:47.142
- Let's go.[cite: 1]
- Let's go![cite: 1]

00:28:51.312 --> 00:28:52.313
Alright.[cite: 1]

00:28:53.481 --> 00:28:54.524
Oh my![cite: 1]

00:28:54.607 --> 00:28:56.025
Oh my god, sir![cite: 1]

00:28:56.109 --> 00:28:58.153
Where are you going?[cite: 1]

00:28:58.236 --> 00:28:59.237
Over there?[cite: 1]

00:28:59.320 --> 00:29:01.114
I understand! Alright.[cite: 1]

00:29:01.197 --> 00:29:03.700
- Let's go![cite: 1]
- Hold on a second![cite: 1]

00:29:04.659 --> 00:29:07.746
- Is he trying to steal the car?[cite: 1]
- Probably not. He's just helping out.[cite: 1]

00:29:07.829 --> 00:29:08.872
Wait for me![cite: 1]

00:29:08.955 --> 00:29:10.582
Let's go![cite: 1]

00:29:10.665 --> 00:29:12.041
Where is he going?[cite: 1]

00:29:14.002 --> 00:29:16.171
Isn't it great

00:29:16.254 --> 00:29:17.714
to be needed by others

00:29:18.506 --> 00:29:19.841
and to help them?[cite: 1]

00:29:20.633 --> 00:29:22.260
In these dark and difficult times,[cite: 1]

00:29:22.343 --> 00:29:24.721
I will be a positive force
and a guiding light.[cite: 1]

00:29:25.346 --> 00:29:28.516
You did a good job today, Park Jin Cheol.[cite: 1]

00:29:34.564 --> 00:29:35.523
ROK MARINE CORPS[cite: 1]
VETERANS ASSOCIATION[cite: 1]

00:29:51.956 --> 00:29:53.416
Copy that. Commencing operation.[cite: 1]

00:29:53.500 --> 00:29:55.960
Unit 911, fall back. I'll take the lead.[cite: 1]

00:29:56.044 --> 00:29:56.878
Throwing grenade.[cite: 1]

00:29:56.961 --> 00:29:58.630
Get out of the way. That's right![cite: 1]

00:29:58.713 --> 00:30:00.673
Get out of the way now. Exactly.[cite: 1]

00:30:00.757 --> 00:30:03.384
Do it like the Marines!
Throw the grenade! Fall back now![cite: 1]

00:30:03.468 --> 00:30:04.302
A bomb![cite: 1]

00:30:06.554 --> 00:30:07.388
ORIGINAL TAEKWONDO[cite: 1]

00:30:10.266 --> 00:30:12.060
Fall back! Fall back now![cite: 1]

00:30:12.143 --> 00:30:14.854
Don't go out! Step aside![cite: 1]

00:30:14.938 --> 00:30:17.649
Hey! Didn't you hear what I just said?[cite: 1]

00:30:17.732 --> 00:30:18.691
Catch them![cite: 1]

00:30:19.317 --> 00:30:20.944
Let me do it![cite: 1]

00:30:21.027 --> 00:30:22.320
Oh, damn it.[cite: 1]

00:30:22.403 --> 00:30:23.279
Wait a minute.[cite: 1]

00:30:24.405 --> 00:30:25.281
Do you hear that?[cite: 1]

00:30:25.949 --> 00:30:27.033
Move quietly.[cite: 1]

00:30:34.541 --> 00:30:38.294
What was that noise? It's a bomb. A bomb![cite: 1]

00:30:45.677 --> 00:30:46.719
Hey.[cite: 1]

00:30:46.803 --> 00:30:47.887
Were you in here?[cite: 1]

00:30:47.971 --> 00:30:49.222
Mission failed.[cite: 1]

00:30:49.848 --> 00:30:53.810
Man, I just kicked a door open,
and now my leg hurts like crazy.[cite: 1]

00:30:53.893 --> 00:30:54.853
Ouch, it hurts so much.[cite: 1]

00:30:58.857 --> 00:31:01.526
What are you looking at?[cite: 1]

00:31:01.609 --> 00:31:03.528
Why don't you greet your senior?[cite: 1]

00:31:03.611 --> 00:31:04.821
This crazy punk...[cite: 1]

00:31:05.905 --> 00:31:07.282
Don't you know how to knock?[cite: 1]

00:31:07.365 --> 00:31:10.326
Why did you kick my office door
like a mule?[cite: 1]

00:31:10.410 --> 00:31:12.036
Where is my doorknob?[cite: 1]

00:31:12.120 --> 00:31:13.913
I knocked on the door, 12 times.[cite: 1]

00:31:13.997 --> 00:31:15.540
You were playing games so you couldn't hear.[cite: 1]

00:31:15.623 --> 00:31:18.626
A Taekwondo master like you
should behave properly.[cite: 1]

00:31:19.127 --> 00:31:21.087
Goodness![cite: 1]

00:31:22.213 --> 00:31:23.631
Everyone, gather around.[cite: 1]

00:31:25.508 --> 00:31:27.010
Are you a kid?[cite: 1]

00:31:30.471 --> 00:31:32.181
This match is really important, you know?[cite: 1]

00:31:32.265 --> 00:31:33.558
Do you want to end up like that door?[cite: 1]

00:31:33.641 --> 00:31:35.727
Mr. Kim should be getting off work soon.[cite: 1]

00:31:35.810 --> 00:31:37.520
Leave now, before I break it.[cite: 1]

00:31:37.604 --> 00:31:39.606
What does him getting off work have to do with me?[cite: 1]

00:31:40.815 --> 00:31:43.776
This is the only day all year
our group gets together![cite: 1]

00:31:45.236 --> 00:31:46.112
Is it today?[cite: 1]

00:31:49.866 --> 00:31:51.159
Seriously, is it today?[cite: 1]

00:31:52.285 --> 00:31:53.369
Oh my god.[cite: 1]

00:31:54.495 --> 00:31:55.830
I must be getting old.[cite: 1]

00:31:55.914 --> 00:31:57.373
I completely forgot.[cite: 1]

00:31:57.457 --> 00:32:00.418
Let's go.
Let's see how old he's gotten.[cite: 1]

00:32:01.210 --> 00:32:02.420
Good lord.[cite: 1]

00:32:02.503 --> 00:32:04.756
Hey, what are you going to do with this?[cite: 1]

00:32:05.256 --> 00:32:06.215
Huh?[cite: 1]

00:32:07.008 --> 00:32:07.967
Just plug it back in.[cite: 1]

00:32:08.676 --> 00:32:10.553
"Just plug it back in"?[cite: 1]

00:32:12.305 --> 00:32:13.473
Can you really just plug it in?[cite: 1]

00:32:18.144 --> 00:32:20.146
Alright.[cite: 1]

00:32:20.730 --> 00:32:22.982
It's ice cold. Drink up.[cite: 1]

00:32:23.066 --> 00:32:24.317
Yeah, pour me a shot of soju.[cite: 1]

00:32:24.901 --> 00:32:25.985
Here.[cite: 1]

00:32:27.695 --> 00:32:31.407
That white Taekwondo uniform
is really bothering my eyes.[cite: 1]

00:32:31.491 --> 00:32:33.201
It's embarrassing. Go sit over there by yourself.[cite: 1]

00:32:33.284 --> 00:32:35.453
I dropped the kids off and came straight here.[cite: 1]

00:32:35.536 --> 00:32:37.330
Don't flip the meat yet.[cite: 1]

00:32:39.374 --> 00:32:41.250
Look who's talking. Look at yourself.[cite: 1]

00:32:41.334 --> 00:32:43.086
Planning to go on a mission right after eating?[cite: 1]

00:32:43.920 --> 00:32:45.880
What's wrong with this outfit? Are you embarrassed?[cite: 1]

00:32:45.964 --> 00:32:48.341
Between the two of us,
who looks more ridiculous?[cite: 1]

00:32:48.424 --> 00:32:51.219
I can just take off my jacket
and I'll be fine.[cite: 1]

00:32:51.302 --> 00:32:52.553
Wow.[cite: 1]

00:32:52.637 --> 00:32:54.055
Look, it's Da Bin. Say hi.[cite: 1]

00:32:54.138 --> 00:32:55.807
- Hi.[cite: 1]
- Hello.[cite: 1]

00:32:57.225 --> 00:32:59.143
I wear this shirt because I miss my daughter.[cite: 1]

00:32:59.227 --> 00:33:01.562
She's always traveling around,[cite: 1]

00:33:01.646 --> 00:33:03.106
so I rarely get to see her.[cite: 1]

00:33:03.690 --> 00:33:05.817
But if I look in the mirror, I can say:[cite: 1]

00:33:05.900 --> 00:33:08.695
"Hey, look who's here.
It's my daughter, Da Bin![cite: 1]

00:33:08.778 --> 00:33:10.488
It's me, dad, so nice to see you.[cite: 1]

00:33:10.571 --> 00:33:12.198
So, are you coming home today?"[cite: 1]

00:33:12.281 --> 00:33:14.492
Da Bin seems embarrassed of you.[cite: 1]

00:33:14.575 --> 00:33:15.785
She can't even lift her head.[cite: 1]

00:33:15.868 --> 00:33:17.453
Let me help her.[cite: 1]

00:33:17.537 --> 00:33:18.371
Hey.[cite: 1]

00:33:18.454 --> 00:33:19.914
You remind me of that door.[cite: 1]

00:33:19.998 --> 00:33:21.582
Need me to teach you a lesson?[cite: 1]

00:33:28.840 --> 00:33:29.716
The meat is burning.[cite: 1]

00:33:32.301 --> 00:33:33.302
You're ridiculous.[cite: 1]

00:33:37.056 --> 00:33:40.226
No answer or anything.
He just walked right past.[cite: 1]

00:33:40.309 --> 00:33:41.686
- Really?[cite: 1]
- Here.[cite: 1]

00:33:41.769 --> 00:33:43.980
- Alright.[cite: 1]
- Let's drink.[cite: 1]

00:33:44.063 --> 00:33:45.273
- Cheers.[cite: 1]
- Cheers.[cite: 1]

00:33:47.942 --> 00:33:52.321
I wonder who Tae Hun takes after
to be so rude.[cite: 1]

00:33:52.405 --> 00:33:53.364
- You.[cite: 1]
- You.[cite: 1]

00:33:53.448 --> 00:33:55.366
Right, I am rude.[cite: 1]

00:34:02.290 --> 00:34:05.168
The alcohol tastes really bitter tonight.[cite: 1]

00:34:05.251 --> 00:34:06.919
But you know what?[cite: 1]

00:34:07.003 --> 00:34:08.880
Raising Da Bin is my reason for living.[cite: 1]

00:34:08.963 --> 00:34:12.175
You guys know, I might not be as strong[cite: 1]

00:34:12.258 --> 00:34:14.260
and successful as I used to be,[cite: 1]

00:34:14.343 --> 00:34:15.678
but I'm satisfied with the present.[cite: 1]

00:34:15.762 --> 00:34:17.513
- This guy.[cite: 1]
- But I have to say,[cite: 1]

00:34:17.597 --> 00:34:19.307
Da Bin is growing up too fast.[cite: 1]

00:34:19.390 --> 00:34:22.101
She used to be
such a cute little kid,[cite: 1]

00:34:22.185 --> 00:34:24.479
but now that she's in high school,
she won't listen to me.[cite: 1]

00:34:24.562 --> 00:34:25.980
Soon enough, she'll meet someone[cite: 1]

00:34:26.898 --> 00:34:28.066
and get married, right?[cite: 1]

00:34:28.691 --> 00:34:31.194
And we'll just grow further apart,
right?[cite: 1]

00:34:32.779 --> 00:34:33.613
Just...[cite: 1]

00:34:34.447 --> 00:34:37.158
Just thinking about it breaks my heart.[cite: 1]

00:34:38.534 --> 00:34:39.535
Oh, Da Bin.[cite: 1]

00:34:40.328 --> 00:34:42.288
Please don't ever leave me.[cite: 1]

00:34:42.371 --> 00:34:45.625
You're not a sucker for your daughter.
You're just a fool.[cite: 1]

00:34:46.918 --> 00:34:47.752
I should get going.[cite: 1]

00:34:47.835 --> 00:34:49.462
- You're leaving already?[cite: 1]
- Already?[cite: 1]

00:34:49.545 --> 00:34:50.630
Min Ji is home alone.[cite: 1]

00:34:50.713 --> 00:34:54.842
Hey, she probably wouldn't even like it
if you went home early anyway.[cite: 1]

00:34:55.593 --> 00:34:57.053
Have a few more drinks before you go.[cite: 1]

00:34:57.136 --> 00:34:58.846
- What's this?[cite: 1]
- Take it back for the kids.[cite: 1]

00:34:58.930 --> 00:35:00.807
- Oh man, come on.[cite: 1]
- You're too polite.[cite: 1]

00:35:00.890 --> 00:35:02.391
- Hey, wait.[cite: 1]
- Hold on a second.[cite: 1]

00:35:02.475 --> 00:35:04.977
Sit down for a bit. Just two more minutes.[cite: 1]

00:35:05.061 --> 00:35:06.479
Don't be so cold.[cite: 1]

00:35:09.190 --> 00:35:10.900
You don't have to do that.[cite: 1]

00:35:13.528 --> 00:35:16.239
Here, Da Bin.
Uncle is giving you some allowance.[cite: 1]

00:35:16.322 --> 00:35:18.407
- Listen, Kim.[cite: 1]
- You should thank him.[cite: 1]

00:35:18.491 --> 00:35:21.452
We should meet up
more often, okay?[cite: 1]

00:35:21.536 --> 00:35:24.288
Seriously,
once a year? That's ridiculous.[cite: 1]

00:35:24.372 --> 00:35:26.707
If we only meet once a year,[cite: 1]

00:35:26.791 --> 00:35:30.378
- we only have about 35 more times left.[cite: 1]
- That's right.[cite: 1]

00:35:30.461 --> 00:35:34.841
I understand your decision
after your wife passed away,[cite: 1]

00:35:34.924 --> 00:35:36.551
but you need to live your own life too.[cite: 1]

00:35:36.634 --> 00:35:40.263
When will you stop making your daughter
the sole purpose of your life?[cite: 1]

00:35:40.346 --> 00:35:42.515
- Min Ji is all grown up now.[cite: 1]
- He's right.[cite: 1]

00:35:42.598 --> 00:35:44.308
She'll get a boyfriend soon.[cite: 1]

00:35:44.392 --> 00:35:45.309
She's still a child.[cite: 1]

00:35:45.393 --> 00:35:48.396
The more you overprotect your kids,[cite: 1]

00:35:48.479 --> 00:35:50.898
the more suffocated they feel.[cite: 1]

00:35:50.982 --> 00:35:53.234
Stop being so annoying![cite: 1]

00:35:54.402 --> 00:35:57.196
Come on, can't we
just eat in peace?[cite: 1]

00:35:57.280 --> 00:35:59.157
That guy is really getting on my nerves![cite: 1]

00:35:59.240 --> 00:36:01.492
- Can you put that cigarette out?[cite: 1]
- Why?[cite: 1]

00:36:01.576 --> 00:36:03.578
This is a rooftop! Why should I put it out?[cite: 1]

00:36:03.661 --> 00:36:05.746
There are other customers here too.[cite: 1]

00:36:05.830 --> 00:36:08.166
What customers? Where?[cite: 1]

00:36:08.916 --> 00:36:10.001
Who?[cite: 1]

00:36:10.543 --> 00:36:11.752
Who?[cite: 1]

00:36:14.630 --> 00:36:16.048
- Stop staring.[cite: 1]
- Looking at what?[cite: 1]

00:36:16.132 --> 00:36:17.842
What? Are you mad?[cite: 1]

00:36:21.470 --> 00:36:23.097
He must be really pissed off.[cite: 1]

00:36:25.224 --> 00:36:26.642
What?[cite: 1]

00:36:27.518 --> 00:36:29.645
Don't. This has
nothing to do with us.[cite: 1]

00:36:29.729 --> 00:36:32.481
We are just middle-aged men who put up with injustice.[cite: 1]

00:36:32.565 --> 00:36:33.774
We aren't young anymore.[cite: 1]

00:36:33.858 --> 00:36:35.818
We're just middle-aged men with glasses.[cite: 1]

00:36:35.902 --> 00:36:36.903
Right?[cite: 1]

00:36:36.986 --> 00:36:39.238
The bill is paid, let's go.[cite: 1]

00:36:39.322 --> 00:36:40.281
Let's go.[cite: 1]

00:36:40.364 --> 00:36:41.365
Stand up.[cite: 1]

00:36:42.617 --> 00:36:44.118
Hey, grunt! Where are you going?[cite: 1]

00:36:44.202 --> 00:36:45.536
- That's enough.[cite: 1]
- Let go of me.[cite: 1]

00:36:45.620 --> 00:36:47.163
Going to scrub the slop buckets?[cite: 1]

00:36:48.122 --> 00:36:50.124
Jin Cheol. You remember, right?[cite: 1]

00:36:50.208 --> 00:36:51.042
Yeah.[cite: 1]

00:36:51.959 --> 00:36:54.337
We're just middle-aged men with glasses.[cite: 1]

00:36:56.088 --> 00:36:57.590
What? Are you scared?[cite: 1]

00:37:00.593 --> 00:37:03.846
You were glaring at me the whole time earlier.[cite: 1]

00:37:03.930 --> 00:37:05.473
Get over here, you bastard![cite: 1]

00:37:05.556 --> 00:37:07.600
Hey grunt.
Why don't you do some exercises?[cite: 1]

00:37:07.683 --> 00:37:08.768
Come on, give me 20 push-ups.[cite: 1]

00:37:09.894 --> 00:37:11.103
One, two![cite: 1]

00:37:11.187 --> 00:37:12.313
What is that?[cite: 1]

00:37:12.396 --> 00:37:14.357
It's embarrassing as hell. Who is this?[cite: 1]

00:37:14.440 --> 00:37:15.691
This girl is pretty![cite: 1]

00:37:16.192 --> 00:37:17.401
So cute.[cite: 1]

00:37:18.653 --> 00:37:20.321
Why don't you introduce her to me?[cite: 1]

00:37:21.155 --> 00:37:22.615
I'll treat her right.[cite: 1]

00:37:22.698 --> 00:37:24.951
It's on, then![cite: 1]

00:37:29.455 --> 00:37:30.289
Jin Cheol.[cite: 1]

00:37:38.214 --> 00:37:39.215
What the hell is that?[cite: 1]

00:37:39.882 --> 00:37:41.634
You fat pig![cite: 1]

00:37:43.678 --> 00:37:45.137
Hey, pig, get up.[cite: 1]

00:37:45.846 --> 00:37:47.098
Let me borrow that bag.[cite: 1]

00:37:51.560 --> 00:37:53.521
Kim, aren't we going to stop him?[cite: 1]

00:37:54.689 --> 00:37:55.898
Where did he go?[cite: 1]

00:37:58.859 --> 00:38:02.071
Did you see a tall guy wearing glasses
and a gloomy black suit?[cite: 1]

00:38:03.281 --> 00:38:04.490
A really tall guy.[cite: 1]

00:38:07.243 --> 00:38:08.119
Hey, Kim...[cite: 1]

00:38:09.787 --> 00:38:10.913
Alright, just go.[cite: 1]

00:38:13.874 --> 00:38:15.126
Are you the police?[cite: 1]

00:38:15.209 --> 00:38:17.169
There's a fight going on here.[cite: 1]

00:38:17.253 --> 00:38:19.422
Yes, a massive fight. Someone is about to die.[cite: 1]

00:38:19.505 --> 00:38:20.840
Please hurry![cite: 1]

00:38:25.428 --> 00:38:28.514
No. That will kill him.
No, don't do that.[cite: 1]

00:38:36.188 --> 00:38:38.566
He should run.
Is he frozen or something?[cite: 1]

00:39:04.842 --> 00:39:06.093
Stop it.[cite: 1]

00:39:06.719 --> 00:39:07.553
Stop it now![cite: 1]

00:39:14.185 --> 00:39:17.063
Officer, shoot something![cite: 1]

00:39:17.146 --> 00:39:19.190
- Shoot your gun![cite: 1]
- Gun?[cite: 1]

00:39:19.273 --> 00:39:21.942
Shoot anything!
Anything! Hurry up![cite: 1]

00:39:24.070 --> 00:39:25.279
Hurry up![cite: 1]

00:39:41.670 --> 00:39:43.589
Whose jacket is this? "Kim Nam Hoon"?[cite: 1]

00:39:43.672 --> 00:39:45.341
- What are you doing?[cite: 1]
- Who is Kim Nam Hoon?[cite: 1]

00:39:45.424 --> 00:39:46.967
I don't know.[cite: 1]

00:39:47.051 --> 00:39:49.095
What's wrong with you?[cite: 1]

00:39:49.762 --> 00:39:50.971
Have a good day.[cite: 1]

00:39:54.892 --> 00:39:57.019
Min Ji is all grown up now.[cite: 1]

00:39:57.103 --> 00:39:58.646
Right. She'll get a boyfriend soon.[cite: 1]

00:39:59.230 --> 00:40:01.315
Does she already have a boyfriend?[cite: 1]

00:40:12.993 --> 00:40:14.036
Hey.[cite: 1]

00:40:14.829 --> 00:40:16.872
Do you know where Kim Nam Hoon is?[cite: 1]

00:40:19.208 --> 00:40:20.042
I'm not sure.[cite: 1]

00:40:26.048 --> 00:40:27.216
I have to return this jacket.[cite: 1]

00:40:35.724 --> 00:40:38.477
- You could've just left it on my desk.[cite: 1]
- What?[cite: 1]

00:40:38.561 --> 00:40:39.979
You were looking for me, right?[cite: 1]

00:40:40.062 --> 00:40:42.440
Oh, I just wanted to thank you.[cite: 1]

00:40:43.816 --> 00:40:45.276
- Is that all?[cite: 1]
- Well...[cite: 1]

00:40:45.359 --> 00:40:46.694
I can give you this.[cite: 1]

00:40:50.948 --> 00:40:52.283
Are you serious? Strawberry milk?[cite: 1]

00:40:52.366 --> 00:40:53.534
Am I a kid?[cite: 1]

00:41:09.842 --> 00:41:11.177
Did you like my post?[cite: 1]

00:41:11.260 --> 00:41:12.094
What?[cite: 1]

00:41:13.220 --> 00:41:14.305
I don't use social media.[cite: 1]

00:41:15.723 --> 00:41:16.932
Oh, really?[cite: 1]

00:41:30.362 --> 00:41:31.489
Then what is this?[cite: 1]

00:41:31.572 --> 00:41:32.656
KIM NAM HOON[cite: 1]

00:41:35.242 --> 00:41:36.327
Can I text you?[cite: 1]

00:41:37.703 --> 00:41:38.537
Yeah.[cite: 1]

00:41:39.163 --> 00:41:40.623
Never mind. You have to text me first.[cite: 1]

00:41:40.706 --> 00:41:41.540
Hey.[cite: 1]

00:41:41.624 --> 00:41:44.126
But you have to reply to me.[cite: 1]

00:41:44.210 --> 00:41:45.252
I'll think about it.[cite: 1]

00:41:45.336 --> 00:41:47.505
- Why? What's there to think about?[cite: 1]
- What?[cite: 1]

00:41:47.588 --> 00:41:49.256
Why can't I think about it?[cite: 1]

00:41:49.340 --> 00:41:52.092
You can't do that.
You told me to text first.[cite: 1]

00:42:07.525 --> 00:42:08.901
Hye Ri wants to see you.[cite: 1]

00:42:10.569 --> 00:42:11.487
Get up.[cite: 1]

00:42:28.921 --> 00:42:29.964
Do you know why you're getting beaten up?[cite: 1]

00:42:31.173 --> 00:42:33.634
Hye Ri is asking you. Answer her.[cite: 1]

00:42:37.888 --> 00:42:38.931
You still don't know?[cite: 1]

00:42:39.014 --> 00:42:42.601
How dare you flirt with Hye Ri's boyfriend,
you sly bitch.[cite: 1]

00:42:42.685 --> 00:42:43.602
I didn't do that.[cite: 1]

00:42:43.686 --> 00:42:45.729
I was just returning his PE uniform.[cite: 1]

00:42:46.814 --> 00:42:50.651
In the first place, why did you
borrow his uniform anyway?[cite: 1]

00:42:51.443 --> 00:42:52.736
Who do you think you are?[cite: 1]

00:42:52.820 --> 00:42:55.281
Why didn't you just wear
your own damn PE uniform?[cite: 1]

00:42:56.407 --> 00:42:58.200
Because you guys threw it in the trash.[cite: 1]

00:43:01.287 --> 00:43:02.788
Don't worry.[cite: 1]

00:43:02.871 --> 00:43:04.373
I have no reason to contact him.[cite: 1]

00:43:05.040 --> 00:43:06.584
I don't want anything to do with you guys.[cite: 1]

00:43:16.844 --> 00:43:19.346
Hey, I think you're misunderstanding something.[cite: 1]

00:43:19.430 --> 00:43:23.350
I'm not mad
because you tried to take my toy.[cite: 1]

00:43:23.434 --> 00:43:25.561
It's because of the foul stench on you.[cite: 1]

00:43:26.395 --> 00:43:28.314
I'm annoyed because it'll rub off on him.[cite: 1]

00:43:29.231 --> 00:43:30.399
She doesn't get it.[cite: 1]

00:43:31.400 --> 00:43:32.318
Hold her down.[cite: 1]

00:43:36.155 --> 00:43:37.406
Stand up.[cite: 1]

00:43:39.450 --> 00:43:42.411
How should I accurately describe this smell?[cite: 1]

00:43:52.880 --> 00:43:55.758
It's like a cheap suit[cite: 1]

00:43:56.842 --> 00:43:59.678
stuffed deep inside a closet...[cite: 1]

00:44:00.888 --> 00:44:01.805
Oh, I know.[cite: 1]

00:44:03.515 --> 00:44:04.933
It's the smell of a motherless child.[cite: 1]

00:44:14.568 --> 00:44:15.694
Hey.[cite: 1]

00:44:15.778 --> 00:44:18.656
- You think you know me so well?[cite: 1]
- You crazy bitch![cite: 1]

00:44:18.739 --> 00:44:20.324
Who the hell do you think you are?[cite: 1]

00:44:21.492 --> 00:44:22.701
Who do you think you are? Huh![cite: 1]

00:44:24.620 --> 00:44:26.955
- Hye Ri, are you okay?[cite: 1]
- What do you think you are?[cite: 1]

00:44:31.752 --> 00:44:33.170
Hey![cite: 1]

00:44:33.253 --> 00:44:35.297
You think you know everything about me?[cite: 1]

00:44:36.090 --> 00:44:38.008
- What the hell do you know?[cite: 1]
- Let go of her![cite: 1]

00:44:38.092 --> 00:44:40.135
- Let go of her![cite: 1]
- Stop![cite: 1]

00:44:40.219 --> 00:44:43.180
That wasn't just a scuffle.
It was assault, Mr. Kim.[cite: 1]

00:44:43.263 --> 00:44:46.266
Min Ji attacked that girl.[cite: 1]

00:44:46.350 --> 00:44:48.769
I'll be right there.[cite: 1]

00:44:48.852 --> 00:44:49.895
Please hurry.[cite: 1]

00:44:50.521 --> 00:44:52.690
I'm about to blow my top.[cite: 1]

00:44:54.441 --> 00:44:55.818
Why did it have to be Hye Ri?[cite: 1]

00:44:55.901 --> 00:45:00.280
The father of the girl who was beaten
is the Chairman of Juhak Construction.[cite: 1]

00:45:00.364 --> 00:45:01.824
You've heard of them, right?[cite: 1]

00:45:05.744 --> 00:45:07.162
Chairman Ju also built[cite: 1]

00:45:07.704 --> 00:45:09.081
this hotel, didn't he?[cite: 1]

00:45:10.874 --> 00:45:11.708
Yes.[cite: 1]

00:45:13.168 --> 00:45:15.462
Back then, my daughter
had just graduated from elementary school,[cite: 1]

00:45:16.547 --> 00:45:17.881
about four years ago.[cite: 1]

00:45:17.965 --> 00:45:21.009
Oh, I see you have a daughter.[cite: 1]

00:45:21.093 --> 00:45:23.679
If she takes after you,
she must be very pretty.[cite: 1]

00:45:24.888 --> 00:45:25.722
You flatter me.[cite: 1]

00:45:26.807 --> 00:45:31.061
By the way, this is my first time
having a meeting at a spa.[cite: 1]

00:45:31.145 --> 00:45:34.523
There's no need to mince words
or hide anything here.[cite: 1]

00:45:36.859 --> 00:45:37.860
Alright, so here's the deal.[cite: 1]

00:45:38.819 --> 00:45:40.904
Let me just ask you straight out.[cite: 1]

00:45:40.988 --> 00:45:44.283
What's in it for me if this
redevelopment project is approved?[cite: 1]

00:45:44.366 --> 00:45:48.120
It will provide a better living environment
for your constituents.[cite: 1]

00:45:48.203 --> 00:45:49.371
And?[cite: 1]

00:45:50.372 --> 00:45:51.623
It will create[cite: 1]

00:45:53.292 --> 00:45:56.044
a more favorable environment
for your political fundraising.[cite: 1]

00:45:57.838 --> 00:45:59.506
Double what you got last time.[cite: 1]

00:46:06.054 --> 00:46:08.140
Alright. Let's work together.[cite: 1]

00:46:08.223 --> 00:46:13.979
There must be something in the water.
I feel so much more refreshed.[cite: 1]

00:46:15.063 --> 00:46:16.648
I should get going now.[cite: 1]

00:46:17.774 --> 00:46:18.817
Take your time.[cite: 1]

00:46:24.031 --> 00:46:25.491
Oh my, Chairman Ju.[cite: 1]

00:46:25.574 --> 00:46:27.242
What happened to your body?[cite: 1]

00:46:27.326 --> 00:46:29.536
It doesn't look very nice, does it?[cite: 1]

00:46:31.497 --> 00:46:34.333
When I was young, I impulsively got some tattoos,[cite: 1]

00:46:35.584 --> 00:46:37.377
but when I started in business, I regretted it.[cite: 1]

00:46:38.086 --> 00:46:39.421
I was embarrassed to show my daughter.[cite: 1]

00:46:40.756 --> 00:46:43.133
So I burned them off myself with a blowtorch.[cite: 1]

00:46:44.134 --> 00:46:46.053
With a blowtorch?[cite: 1]

00:46:46.678 --> 00:46:49.097
Why didn't you go to a hospital to get them removed?[cite: 1]

00:46:50.265 --> 00:46:53.602
I saw it as a commitment
to never return to my old life.[cite: 1]

00:46:53.685 --> 00:46:57.689
But still, doing that must have been incredibly painful.[cite: 1]

00:47:00.359 --> 00:47:03.987
It's nothing compared to what I've done
to get this far.[cite: 1]

00:47:04.571 --> 00:47:05.405
The greater pain...[cite: 1]

00:47:07.699 --> 00:47:10.285
is when people
don't keep their promises to me[cite: 1]

00:47:10.369 --> 00:47:12.120
and just disappear.[cite: 1]

00:47:18.710 --> 00:47:20.337
I'm counting on you, Assemblyman Sim.[cite: 1]

00:47:20.420 --> 00:47:22.256
Alright, yes, of course.[cite: 1]

00:47:28.512 --> 00:47:30.764
Chairman, your wife is calling.[cite: 1]

00:47:36.270 --> 00:47:38.397
- What is it?[cite: 1]
- Honey, something terrible has happened.[cite: 1]

00:47:38.480 --> 00:47:39.690
Hye Ri...[cite: 1]

00:47:39.773 --> 00:47:43.277
Hye Ri was just assaulted at school![cite: 1]

00:47:44.903 --> 00:47:45.821
Got it.[cite: 1]

00:47:50.325 --> 00:47:51.285
To Hye Ri's school.[cite: 1]

00:47:51.910 --> 00:47:53.161
Yes, Chairman.[cite: 1]

00:48:18.437 --> 00:48:19.688
You can't go in.[cite: 1]

00:48:21.815 --> 00:48:24.943
The Chairman himself told me to come,
you bastard.[cite: 1]

00:48:25.027 --> 00:48:26.320
Hey, Nam.[cite: 1]

00:48:27.112 --> 00:48:28.113
What's their problem?[cite: 1]

00:48:28.196 --> 00:48:29.156
Keep it down.[cite: 1]

00:48:30.157 --> 00:48:31.700
The Chairman is inside.[cite: 1]

00:48:34.995 --> 00:48:35.871
You told me to come.[cite: 1]

00:48:35.954 --> 00:48:37.372
So I came.[cite: 1]

00:48:37.456 --> 00:48:38.790
There's a slight change of plans.[cite: 1]

00:48:39.541 --> 00:48:40.792
I'll call you back.[cite: 1]

00:48:45.047 --> 00:48:48.675
Am I your hunting dog or something
that you can just order me around?[cite: 1]

00:48:56.183 --> 00:48:57.351
I thought you knew.[cite: 1]

00:48:57.976 --> 00:48:58.977
No, I didn't know.[cite: 1]

00:49:05.275 --> 00:49:06.485
I didn't know.[cite: 1]

00:49:08.570 --> 00:49:09.821
This hound is leaving.[cite: 1]

00:49:11.823 --> 00:49:13.575
Damn it.[cite: 1]

00:49:16.536 --> 00:49:18.330
When is he finally going to get here?[cite: 1]

00:49:20.749 --> 00:49:22.000
Let's go, Hye Ri.[cite: 1]

00:49:22.084 --> 00:49:24.586
How dare he make us wait?[cite: 1]

00:49:25.212 --> 00:49:26.129
Sit down.[cite: 1]

00:49:27.172 --> 00:49:28.465
At least meet him first.[cite: 1]

00:49:33.428 --> 00:49:36.306
What took you so long?[cite: 1]

00:49:43.897 --> 00:49:47.359
How on earth did you raise your child
for her to behave like this?[cite: 1]

00:49:48.318 --> 00:49:49.986
Look at my daughter![cite: 1]

00:49:50.070 --> 00:49:52.489
How can I send her to school now?[cite: 1]

00:49:53.365 --> 00:49:54.491
Why aren't you looking at her?[cite: 1]

00:49:55.075 --> 00:49:57.661
Take a good look![cite: 1]

00:50:02.499 --> 00:50:03.542
I am sorry.[cite: 1]

00:50:03.625 --> 00:50:06.128
I've only heard
about school violence and bullying.[cite: 1]

00:50:06.211 --> 00:50:10.215
I never thought Hye Ri would be in the same class
with someone like her![cite: 1]

00:50:10.298 --> 00:50:12.467
Dad, I didn't do anything wrong.[cite: 1]

00:50:12.551 --> 00:50:14.428
She and her friends kept harassing me.[cite: 1]

00:50:14.511 --> 00:50:16.763
I held back as much as I could before fighting back![cite: 1]

00:50:16.847 --> 00:50:17.764
Kim Min Ji.[cite: 1]

00:50:19.558 --> 00:50:20.475
Be quiet.[cite: 1]

00:50:20.559 --> 00:50:22.769
But she was the one who hit me first![cite: 1]

00:50:22.853 --> 00:50:23.687
You don't believe me?[cite: 1]

00:50:24.521 --> 00:50:25.355
Min Ji.[cite: 1]

00:50:27.733 --> 00:50:32.529
Mr. Kim, I think
you should come to a settlement with the victims.[cite: 1]

00:50:32.612 --> 00:50:34.948
No, forget it.[cite: 1]

00:50:35.031 --> 00:50:37.200
I demand a disciplinary hearing[cite: 1]

00:50:37.284 --> 00:50:38.994
and want this on her permanent record.[cite: 1]

00:50:45.625 --> 00:50:47.169
Dad![cite: 1]

00:50:51.965 --> 00:50:53.592
Do you have no self-respect?[cite: 1]

00:50:54.509 --> 00:50:55.343
I am sorry.[cite: 1]

00:50:55.427 --> 00:50:57.220
I haven't done a good job as a parent[cite: 1]

00:50:58.054 --> 00:50:59.347
because I have to raise her alone.[cite: 1]

00:51:00.015 --> 00:51:02.434
As fellow parents raising daughters,[cite: 1]

00:51:02.517 --> 00:51:04.895
I hope you can
find it in your hearts to forgive us.[cite: 1]

00:51:07.230 --> 00:51:08.857
As her father, I will take responsibility,[cite: 1]

00:51:10.525 --> 00:51:11.526
and have her transfer schools.[cite: 1]

00:51:11.610 --> 00:51:12.694
Dad![cite: 1]

00:51:19.284 --> 00:51:21.203
As fellow parents raising daughters?[cite: 1]

00:51:32.172 --> 00:51:33.006
Right.[cite: 1]

00:51:36.843 --> 00:51:38.470
Raising a daughter isn't easy.[cite: 1]

00:51:43.099 --> 00:51:44.184
Especially all alone.[cite: 1]

00:51:46.895 --> 00:51:49.064
Growing up without a mother
must be very difficult.[cite: 1]

00:51:50.315 --> 00:51:52.818
It's normal for kids to argue and fight
while growing up.[cite: 1]

00:51:56.488 --> 00:51:57.864
You've apologized to us,[cite: 1]

00:51:57.948 --> 00:51:59.866
so just take care of the school transfer.[cite: 1]

00:51:59.950 --> 00:52:00.784
- Dad![cite: 1]
- Honey![cite: 1]

00:52:00.867 --> 00:52:01.952
Let's stop here.[cite: 1]

00:52:05.080 --> 00:52:05.914
Thank you.[cite: 1]

00:52:17.801 --> 00:52:18.635
Min Ji.[cite: 1]

00:52:21.179 --> 00:52:22.389
Kim Min Ji.[cite: 1]

00:52:23.348 --> 00:52:24.182
KIM NAM HOON[cite: 1]

00:52:37.571 --> 00:52:39.573
What does her father do?[cite: 1]

00:52:40.198 --> 00:52:43.702
It seems he's just an
ordinary office worker.[cite: 1]

00:52:43.785 --> 00:52:47.330
Thank you for your leniency, Chairman Ju.[cite: 1]

00:52:48.039 --> 00:52:51.084
Thank you. This
will never happen again.[cite: 1]

00:52:53.461 --> 00:52:54.421
Of course.[cite: 1]

00:52:54.504 --> 00:52:56.548
Because if something like this happens again,[cite: 1]

00:52:58.008 --> 00:53:00.010
this school and all of you will disappear.[cite: 1]

00:53:19.112 --> 00:53:19.988
Min Ji.[cite: 1]

00:53:22.073 --> 00:53:23.116
Are you hungry?[cite: 1]

00:53:24.242 --> 00:53:25.368
Should we go grab something to eat?[cite: 1]

00:53:27.662 --> 00:53:28.538
Min Ji.[cite: 1]

00:53:29.623 --> 00:53:30.624
Kim Min Ji.[cite: 1]

00:53:34.920 --> 00:53:36.671
Why didn't you believe me?[cite: 1]

00:53:37.505 --> 00:53:38.882
Of course I believe you.[cite: 1]

00:53:38.965 --> 00:53:41.134
Then why do I have to transfer schools?[cite: 1]

00:53:41.217 --> 00:53:42.886
I didn't do anything wrong.[cite: 1]

00:53:45.639 --> 00:53:47.891
Why did you have to bow down and beg?[cite: 1]

00:53:48.475 --> 00:53:50.518
Is it because Hye Ri's dad is powerful?[cite: 1]

00:53:51.269 --> 00:53:52.854
I'm so embarrassed.[cite: 1]

00:53:53.855 --> 00:53:56.733
I feel angry, frustrated,
and pathetic too.[cite: 1]

00:53:57.817 --> 00:53:59.569
What have you done with your life?[cite: 1]

00:54:01.196 --> 00:54:03.782
Her dad is a rich chairman
with lots of connections,[cite: 1]

00:54:04.574 --> 00:54:07.202
but why are you just a
lowly office worker?[cite: 1]

00:54:08.411 --> 00:54:10.121
Why did you even give birth to me?[cite: 1]

00:54:11.998 --> 00:54:12.832
Min Ji.[cite: 1]

00:54:12.916 --> 00:54:13.959
As your father...[cite: 1]

00:54:16.002 --> 00:54:17.170
As your father...[cite: 1]

00:54:24.010 --> 00:54:26.680
As your father,
you are my whole world.[cite: 1]

00:54:27.639 --> 00:54:28.932
I don't have a mom.[cite: 1]

00:54:29.516 --> 00:54:31.101
I only have you,[cite: 1]

00:54:32.310 --> 00:54:34.062
but if you don't take my side...[cite: 1]

00:54:34.145 --> 00:54:36.147
They are the bad guys.[cite: 1]

00:54:36.773 --> 00:54:39.651
You should have been
the one to trust me the most.[cite: 1]

00:54:44.656 --> 00:54:45.573
Let's go home.[cite: 1]

00:54:45.657 --> 00:54:47.158
I don't want to be with you.[cite: 1]

00:54:47.242 --> 00:54:49.786
I'm staying at Hye Ryeong's tonight,[cite: 1]

00:54:49.869 --> 00:54:51.162
so don't call me.[cite: 1]

00:54:51.246 --> 00:54:52.747
If you call me,[cite: 1]

00:54:53.957 --> 00:54:55.709
I'm running away from home.[cite: 1]

00:54:57.669 --> 00:54:58.586
Min Ji.[cite: 1]

00:55:00.422 --> 00:55:02.007
Tomorrow is your birthday.[cite: 1]

00:55:02.841 --> 00:55:03.675
Kim Min Ji![cite: 1]

00:55:11.307 --> 00:55:13.226
I hate my birthday.[cite: 1]

00:55:16.813 --> 00:55:18.481
It's the day Mom died.[cite: 1]

00:55:52.057 --> 00:55:53.308
THE LATE IM YU JIN[cite: 1]

00:56:15.038 --> 00:56:17.082
This is your favorite flower.[cite: 1]

00:56:17.665 --> 00:56:18.875
They call it honeysuckle.[cite: 1]

00:56:19.375 --> 00:56:20.919
Its meaning is beautiful too.[cite: 1]

00:56:21.961 --> 00:56:23.088
Do you know what it is?[cite: 1]

00:56:23.671 --> 00:56:24.506
What is it?[cite: 1]

00:56:25.173 --> 00:56:26.007
Love and...[cite: 1]

00:56:26.841 --> 00:56:27.801
- devotion.[cite: 1]
- Devotion.[cite: 1]

00:56:33.848 --> 00:56:36.392
I'm sorry, Yu Jin.[cite: 1]

00:57:40.582 --> 00:57:42.125
I have something to tell you.[cite: 1]

00:57:42.208 --> 00:57:44.169
I'll be waiting at the back gate of the school.[cite: 1]

00:57:44.252 --> 00:57:45.712
I'll wait until you come.[cite: 1]

00:58:28.588 --> 00:58:31.925
DAD[cite: 1]

00:58:33.885 --> 00:58:36.846
The number you have dialed
cannot be reached...[cite: 1]

00:58:37.889 --> 00:58:39.599
I don't want to be with you.[cite: 1]

00:58:40.308 --> 00:58:42.435
I'm staying at Hye Ryeong's tonight,[cite: 1]

00:58:42.519 --> 00:58:43.811
so don't call me.[cite: 1]

00:58:45.188 --> 00:58:46.356
If you call me,[cite: 1]

00:58:47.565 --> 00:58:49.150
I'm running away from home.[cite: 1]

00:59:18.012 --> 00:59:21.766
The number you have dialed is currently turned off.
You will be redirected to...[cite: 1]

00:59:36.155 --> 00:59:37.407
Hello?[cite: 1]

00:59:37.490 --> 00:59:38.324
Hello?[cite: 1]

00:59:39.117 --> 00:59:40.410
Is this Kang Hye Ryeong?[cite: 1]

00:59:40.493 --> 00:59:42.287
Yes. Who is this?[cite: 1]

00:59:42.370 --> 00:59:44.330
This is Min Ji's dad.[cite: 1]

00:59:44.414 --> 00:59:47.792
Huh? How do you know
my phone number?[cite: 1]

00:59:49.335 --> 00:59:51.170
Min Ji told me.[cite: 1]

00:59:51.963 --> 00:59:54.632
Hye Ryeong, is it possible[cite: 1]

00:59:54.716 --> 00:59:56.509
that you were with Min Ji last night?[cite: 1]

00:59:56.593 --> 00:59:57.552
No.[cite: 1]

00:59:59.512 --> 01:00:02.515
So you haven't heard anything from her?[cite: 1]

01:00:02.599 --> 01:00:04.017
No.[cite: 1]

01:00:04.100 --> 01:00:05.268
I'm hanging up now.[cite: 1]

01:00:33.630 --> 01:00:35.506
Hello, I'm Min Ji's dad.[cite: 1]

01:00:36.090 --> 01:00:37.300
Have you seen her?[cite: 1]

01:00:40.720 --> 01:00:43.264
No, she hasn't come to school yet.[cite: 1]

01:00:52.940 --> 01:00:54.108
Kim Nam Hoon?[cite: 1]

01:00:55.109 --> 01:00:57.612
Did you see Min Ji yesterday?[cite: 1]

01:00:59.280 --> 01:01:02.241
I didn't send that message to her.[cite: 1]

01:01:02.867 --> 01:01:04.327
It was those thugs...[cite: 1]

01:01:05.453 --> 01:01:07.455
I only heard them mention the school's back gate.[cite: 1]

01:01:08.373 --> 01:01:09.499
I'm sorry.[cite: 1]

01:01:10.416 --> 01:01:12.543
I couldn't do anything[cite: 1]

01:01:12.627 --> 01:01:14.003
because they snatched my phone.[cite: 1]

01:02:24.282 --> 01:02:27.827
How on earth did you raise your child
for her to behave like this?[cite: 1]

01:03:04.572 --> 01:03:06.491
We just have to pretend we don't know anything.[cite: 1]

01:03:06.574 --> 01:03:08.618
I told everyone to keep quiet, so don't worry.[cite: 1]

01:03:08.701 --> 01:03:11.245
- But who knows.[cite: 1]
- Just trust me.[cite: 1]

01:03:11.329 --> 01:03:12.997
I'm not just some average thug.[cite: 1]

01:03:14.957 --> 01:03:16.501
Hey, it's all cleaned up.[cite: 1]

01:03:17.084 --> 01:03:19.128
See? Even the weather is on our side.[cite: 1]

01:03:20.588 --> 01:03:23.049
If someone reported this,
the police would be here already.[cite: 1]

01:03:23.132 --> 01:03:24.217
No one will find her.[cite: 1]

01:03:24.300 --> 01:03:26.093
Didn't you say her dad is just a pathetic loser?[cite: 1]

01:03:27.094 --> 01:03:29.806
- Can I ask you a question?[cite: 1]
- Shit, you startled me![cite: 1]

01:03:30.348 --> 01:03:32.809
I'm Min Ji's dad.[cite: 1]

01:03:33.935 --> 01:03:36.187
We don't know where she is,
so just leave.[cite: 1]

01:03:37.271 --> 01:03:39.440
I never said I was looking for her.[cite: 1]

01:03:44.612 --> 01:03:47.406
This is your hair tie, right?[cite: 1]

01:03:47.490 --> 01:03:48.449
It fell on the ground.[cite: 1]

01:03:52.787 --> 01:03:56.457
I told you to get lost,
unless you want to get beaten to a pulp![cite: 1]

01:03:56.541 --> 01:03:58.793
- Is this yours?[cite: 1]
- Damn it.[cite: 1]

01:04:08.845 --> 01:04:09.971
Look at you.[cite: 1]

01:04:11.180 --> 01:04:13.558
- Your time is really up.[cite: 1]
- I'll ask you one last time.[cite: 1]

01:04:14.976 --> 01:04:16.644
- Where is Min Ji?[cite: 1]
- Hey, old man.[cite: 1]

01:04:16.727 --> 01:04:17.854
What do you think?[cite: 1]

01:04:18.437 --> 01:04:19.313
Huh?[cite: 1]

01:04:19.397 --> 01:04:21.148
Do you realize you're dead meat?[cite: 1]

01:04:25.361 --> 01:04:28.030
Who the hell do you think you are?[cite: 1]

01:04:28.114 --> 01:04:29.073
Think you're special?[cite: 1]

01:04:29.156 --> 01:04:31.951
If you're so tough, show it.
Take off your clothes and let's fight.[cite: 1]

01:04:32.034 --> 01:04:33.703
Want me to take them off for you?[cite: 1]

01:04:35.913 --> 01:04:36.914
Let me go![cite: 1]

01:04:37.790 --> 01:04:39.458
Put the gun down.[cite: 1]

01:04:40.167 --> 01:04:41.669
Let me be discharged.[cite: 1]

01:04:42.795 --> 01:04:44.714
Let me be discharged right now![cite: 1]

01:04:50.928 --> 01:04:51.846
We can't do that.[cite: 1]

01:04:51.929 --> 01:04:53.556
Commander, you know as well as I do.[cite: 1]

01:04:53.639 --> 01:04:56.475
No one is allowed to know
of his existence.[cite: 1]

01:04:56.559 --> 01:04:58.352
Code name 66.[cite: 1]

01:04:58.436 --> 01:04:59.854
A North Korean defector[cite: 1]

01:04:59.937 --> 01:05:01.814
recruited by South Korean intelligence.[cite: 1]

01:05:01.898 --> 01:05:03.566
Acted as a double agent five times,[cite: 1]

01:05:03.649 --> 01:05:05.610
carried out 17 infiltration missions into the North.[cite: 1]

01:05:05.693 --> 01:05:09.071
He commanded the assassination operation
against the North Korean Supreme Leader,[cite: 1]

01:05:09.155 --> 01:05:12.325
causing China and Russia
to send tracking teams.[cite: 1]

01:05:14.243 --> 01:05:15.119
What the hell?[cite: 1]

01:05:36.432 --> 01:05:38.768
Letting someone like him be discharged
is unthinkable.[cite: 1]

01:05:38.851 --> 01:05:41.646
If the North finds out he's alive,[cite: 1]

01:05:41.729 --> 01:05:43.356
just his existence alone...[cite: 1]

01:05:44.440 --> 01:05:45.858
would cause a diplomatic crisis.[cite: 1]

01:05:52.782 --> 01:05:53.991
Tell me.[cite: 1]

01:05:55.576 --> 01:05:56.577
Where is Min Ji?[cite: 1]

01:06:37.868 --> 01:06:41.497
AGENT KIM: REBOOT[cite: 1]

01:06:42.248 --> 01:06:43.624
- The law?[cite: 1]
- Who the hell are you?[cite: 1]

01:06:44.834 --> 01:06:45.668
I guess...[cite: 1]

01:06:48.671 --> 01:06:50.339
I'll just be a defector uncle.[cite: 1]

01:06:50.923 --> 01:06:53.342
The government denies
Agent Kim's existence.[cite: 1]

01:06:53.426 --> 01:06:54.552
Arm the infiltration team.[cite: 1]

01:06:55.803 --> 01:06:56.846
Hey, you![cite: 1]

01:06:58.055 --> 01:07:00.266
Is that bastard sleeping?[cite: 1]

01:07:00.349 --> 01:07:01.517
In this situation?[cite: 1]

01:07:02.059 --> 01:07:04.437
I'm letting you live
only because I believe my daughter is still alive.[cite: 1]

01:07:07.148 --> 01:07:08.941
- Dad![cite: 1]
- Is that you, Min Ji?[cite: 1]

01:07:10.818 --> 01:07:12.319
I already disposed of her body.[cite: 1]

01:07:14.864 --> 01:07:19.577
Translator: Trang Nguyen[cite: 1]